https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=13289	12960
<a href="http://yi-it.com/blog/index.php">躺藤椅晒太阳看书</a> 写道 "谷歌宣布<a href="http://www.readwriteweb.com/archives/google_opens_up_its_epub_archive_download_1_million_books_for_free.php">开放EPUB格式的图书存档</a>(<a href="http://www.yeeyan.com/articles/view/11302/56615">译言</a>)：100万本<a href="http://books.google.com/">电子书</a>可免费下载。<i>
